{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Erstelle eine vollständige, professionelle und moderne Website-Struktur und Texte für eine Marke namens SCHNAPPIX 24/7.
    SCHNAPPIX 24/7 ist ein modernes 24/7-Selbstbedienungskonzept mit Premium-Snackautomaten, Getränkeautomaten, Vape- & Hygieneautomaten und Trendprodukten aus Korea, Japan und den USA.
    Die Automaten stehen an öffentlichen Plätzen, Bahnhöfen, Clubs, Schulen, Tankstellen, Wohngebieten und eröffnen moderne 24/7 Mini-Stores.
    
    ⸻
    
    Ziele der Website
    	•	Sofort erklären, was SCHNAPPIX ist
    	•	Vertrauen schaffen
    	•	Standorte präsentieren
    	•	Sortiment (Snacks, Drinks, Trends, Hygiene, Vapes) zeigen
    	•	Firmenkunden (B2B) gewinnen
    	•	Kontaktanfragen generieren
    
    ⸻
    
    Designstil
    	•	Modern, urban, clean
    	•	Schwarzer Hintergrund mit Neon-Elementen
    	•	Farbpalette: Schwarz (#0A0A0A), Neon-Blau (#1B9CFF), Neon-Pink (#FF2DAA), Weiß (#FFFFFF)
    	•	Schrift: Montserrat für Überschriften, Inter für Texte
    	•	Wording: Direkt, zuverlässig, modern, vertrauenswürdig
    
    ⸻
    
    Bitte erstellen:
    
    1. Startseite
    
    Mit klaren Bausteinen:
    	•	Hero-Section: starke Headline + Subline + Buttons
    	•	Vorteil-Section (24/7, Premium-Produkte, sichere Bezahlung, Videoüberwachung)
    	•	Produktkategorien (Snacks, Drinks, Asia/US-Trends, Hygiene, Vapes)
    	•	Standortübersicht (funktioniert als Section)
    	•	Fotos der Automaten
    	•	Kundenbewertungen
    	•	CTA: „Standort ansehen“, „Automat für Firma anfragen“
    
    ⸻
    
    2. Standort-Seite
    	•	Listung aller Automatenstandorte
    	•	Buttons: „Google Maps öffnen“
    	•	Kleine Beschreibung je Standort
    	•	Hinweis auf 24/7 & Sortimentsvariationen
    
    ⸻
    
    3. Produkte / Sortiment
    
    Erstelle Kategorie-Abschnitte:
    	•	Snacks
    	•	Getränke
    	•	Energy & Functional
    	•	Japan/Korea/USA Trendprodukte
    	•	Hygiene & Convenience
    	•	Vapes (mit Hinweis Altersverifikation PAX)
    
    Jede Kategorie soll eine kurze, moderne Beschreibung bekommen.
    
    ⸻
    
    4. B2B / Geschäftskunden
    
    Erstelle eine komplette B2B-Seite:
    	•	Warum ein SCHNAPPIX-Automat?
    	•	Angebot: „Automat kostenlos aufstellen lassen“
    	•	Vorteile für Firmenkunden
    	•	Kurz
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .schnappix-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    min-height: {{ block.settings.section_height }}px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{ block.settings.bg_color_1 }} 0%, {{ block.settings.bg_color_2 }} 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 60px 20px;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="100" height="100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><pattern id="grid" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 100 0 L 0 0 0 100" fill="none" stroke="rgba(27,156,255,0.1)" stroke-width="1"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(%23grid)"/></svg>');
    opacity: 0.3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1200px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: {{ block.settings.badge_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.badge_text_color }};
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.neon_blue }};
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px {{ block.settings.neon_blue }}40;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    background: {{ block.settings.neon_blue }};
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size }}px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} .neon-accent {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{ block.settings.neon_blue }} 0%, {{ block.settings.neon_pink }} 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-subline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subline_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_radius }}px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{ block.settings.neon_blue }} 0%, {{ block.settings.neon_pink }} 100%);
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_btn_text_color }};
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px {{ block.settings.neon_blue }}40;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 30px {{ block.settings.neon_blue }}60;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: {{ block.settings.secondary_btn_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.secondary_btn_text_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.neon_blue }};
  }

  .schnappix-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background: {{ block.settings.neon_blue }};
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_btn_text_color }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .schnappix-hero-features-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 60px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: {{ block.settings.feature_text_color }};
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .schnappix-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: {{ block.settings.neon_blue }}20;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.neon_blue }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .schnappix-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      min-height: {{ block.settings.section_height | times: 0.7 }}px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .schnappix-hero-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .schnappix-hero-subline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subline_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .schnappix-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .schnappix-hero-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .schnappix-hero-features-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="schnappix-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="schnappix-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.show_badge %}
      <div class="schnappix-hero-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <span class="schnappix-hero-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <svg width="8" height="8" viewBox="0 0 8 8" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="4" fill="white"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        {{ block.settings.badge_text }}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.headline != blank %}
      <h1 class="schnappix-hero-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.headline_part1 }} <span class="neon-accent">{{ block.settings.headline_accent }}</span> {{ block.settings.headline_part2 }}
      </h1>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.subline != blank %}
      <p class="schnappix-hero-subline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.subline }}
      </p>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="schnappix-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.primary_btn_text != blank %}
        <a href="{{ block.settings.primary_btn_link }}" class="schnappix-hero-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} schnappix-hero-btn-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.primary_btn_text }}
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M7.5 15L12.5 10L7.5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.secondary_btn_text != blank %}
        <a href="{{ block.settings.secondary_btn_link }}" class="schnappix-hero-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} schnappix-hero-btn-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.secondary_btn_text }}
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    {% if block.settings.show_features %}
      <div class="schnappix-hero-features-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.feature_1_text != blank %}
          <div class="schnappix-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <span class="schnappix-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M11.6667 3.5L5.25 9.91667L2.33333 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            {{ block.settings.feature_1_text }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.feature_2_text != blank %}
          <div class="schnappix-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <span class="schnappix-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M11.6667 3.5L5.25 9.91667L2.33333 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            {{ block.settings.feature_2_text }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.feature_3_text != blank %}
          <div class="schnappix-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <span class="schnappix-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M11.6667 3.5L5.25 9.91667L2.33333 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            {{ block.settings.feature_3_text }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>

